title: $6500-5/3 Weston Lakefront 2 Story Executive Home-3 Car Garage-Fenced
neighborhood: Weston - North of Griffin Rd - West of I-75
posting_body: ['Beautiful updated 5 Bedroom, 3 bath home on the end of a cul-de-sac.', 'Located in the exclusive gated community Emerald Estates.', 'Updated Kitchen with S/S appliances, Quartz counter top, white wood cabinets.', 'Updated bathrooms.', 'This home is scheduled to have a NEW ROOF in a week.', 'This pie shaped lot gives you expansive views of the lake and the utmost privacy.', 'Property comes with new dryer, freshly painted, will be rented with a desk located in one of the bedrooms.', 'Main Access from Weston Rd.', 'Fast access to I-75, Sawgrass expressway and 595.', 'Pet ok w/ landlord approval and deposit.', 'Community boasts a community pool, gym, playground and security.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease, background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 2.5-3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
